ip due to league reorganization</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n|'''1938-39''' \t\n|[[D\u0105b Katowice]] \t\n|[[Warszawianka (ice hockey)|Warszawianka]] \t\n|[[Ognisko Wilno]]\n|-\n|'''1940\u201345''' \t\n|<ref>No championship due to [[World War II]]</ref>\n|\t\n|\n|-\n|'''1945-46''' \t\n|[[KS Cracovia (ice hockey)|KS Cracovia]]\t\n|[[\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a (ice hockey)|\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a]] \t\n|[[Si\u0142a Giszowiec]]\n|-\n|'''1946-47''' \t\n|[[KS Cracovia (ice hockey)|KS Cracovia]]\t\n|[[TS Wis\u0142a Krak\u00f3w|Wis\u0142a Krak\u00f3w]] \t\n|[[\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a (ice hockey)|\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a]]\n|-\n|'''1947-48'''\n|[[KS Cracovia (ice hockey)|KS Cracovia]]\n|<ref>Due to climate conditions, the championship was abandoned</ref>\n|\n|-\n|'''1948-49'''\t\n|[[KS Cracovia (ice hockey)|KS Cracovia]]\t\n|[[KTH Krynica]] \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]]\n|-\n|'''1949-50''' \t\n|[[KTH Krynica]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Jan\u00f3w]] \t\n|[[TKH Toru\u0144|Kolejarz Toru\u0144]]\n|-\n|'''1950-51'''\t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[KTH Krynica]] \t\n|[[KS Cracovia (ice hockey)|KS Cracovia]]\n|-\n|'''1951-52''' \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Jan\u00f3w]] \t\n|[[KTH Krynica]]\n|-\n|'''1952-53''' \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[KTH Krynica]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Jan\u00f3w]]\n|-\n|'''1953-54'''\t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[Gwardia Bydgoszcz]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Jan\u00f3w]]\n|-\n|'''1954-55'''\t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[Gwardia Bydgoszcz]]\t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]]\n|-\n|'''1955-56'''\t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]] \t\n|[[Start Katowice]]\n|-\n|'''1956-57'''\t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]] \t\n|[[Krynickie Towarzystwo Hokejowe|KTH Krynica]]\n|-\n|'''1957-58'''\t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]] \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (hokej na lodzie)|Legia Warszawa]]\t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]]\n|-\n|'''1958-59'''\t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]] \t\n|[[\u0141KS (ice hockey)|\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a]]\n|-\n|'''1959-60''' \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]] \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]]\n|-\n|'''1960-61''' \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]] \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]]\n|-\n|'''1961-62'''\t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]] \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]]\n|-\n|'''1962-63'''\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]]\t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]] \t\n|[[G\u00f3rnik Katowice]]\n|-\n|'''1963-64''' \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]]\t\n|[[Polonia Bydgoszcz (ice hockey)|Polonia Bydgoszcz]]\n|-\n|'''1964-65'''\n|[[GKS Katowice (ice hockey)|GKS Katowice]] \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[Polonia Bydgoszcz (ice hockey)|Polonia Bydgoszcz]]\n|-\n|'''1965-66''' \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]] \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]] \t\n|[[GKS Katowice (ice hockey)|GKS Katowice]]\n|-\n|'''1966-67''' \t\n|[[Legia Warszawa (ice hockey)|Legia Warszawa]]\n|[[GKS Katowice (ice hockey)|GKS Katowice]] \t\n|[[TKH Toru\u0144|Pomorzanin Toru\u0144]]\n|-\n|'''1967-68''' \t\n|[[GKS Katowice (ice hockey)|GKS Katowice]] \t\n|[[TKH Toru\u0144|Pomorzanin Toru\u0144]] \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]]\n|-\n|'''1968-69''' \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]] \t\n|[[GKS Katowice (ice hockey)|GKS Katowice]] \t\n|[[TKH Toru\u0144|Pomorzanin Toru\u0144]]\n|-\n|'''1969-70'''\t\n|[[GKS Katowice (ice hockey)|GKS Katowice]] \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]] \t\n|[[KS Baildon Katowice]]\n|-\n|'''1970-71''' \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]] \t\n|[[Naprz\u00f3d Jan\u00f3w]] \t\n|[[\u0141KS (ice hockey)|\u0141KS \u0141\u00f3d\u017a]]\n|-\n|'''1971-72''' \t\n|[[Podhale Nowy Targ]] \t\n|[[KS Baildon Kat